{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDE0MDYzMjYz", "number": 1422, "title": "Bugfix/added a scroll bar to feedback editor", "bodyText": "Checklist\n\n I tested all changes and all related features with different users (student, tutor, instructor, admin) on the test server https://artemistest.ase.in.tum.de. (Tested it on localhost)\n Client: I added multiple screenshots/screencasts of my UI changes\n\nMotivation and Context\nThis change solves #1397 by expanding the text area to the size of its content.\nDescription\n\nI added the function textareaAutogrow() in ngAfterViewInit() for expanding the feedback textarea to the fitting size.\nSteps for Testing\n\nPrecondition: You have created a text exercise, which is ready for assessment\n\nLog in to Artemis\nNavigate to Course Management\nWrite multiple lines of text in it\nSave the assessment and go back to the dashboard\nReopen the assessment\nThe textbox for feedback should still show all lines of feedback\n\nScreenshots\nAfter reopening an assesment with use of multiple lines of feedback, it should look like this.", "createdAt": "2020-05-06T12:25:10Z", "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/pull/1422", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "cb9f3e528009eca071a837de0e2d6ec3b413ef5a"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-05-12T15:34:06Z", "author": {"login": "tessaRuckstuhl"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 17, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcenmH-gH2gAyNDE0MDYzMjYzOjg2ODAzNTQ0ODc4ZWQxN2E2MDI4YzU0Yjc1MWU3OWE1YjFmY2Q3M2I=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcgmFM8AH2gAyNDE0MDYzMjYzOmU2ODkwM2JlNjViNDNjM2E0YmRhZmE5ZjIzMjdlNDQ1ZTQ0NzNmOWU=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "86803544878ed17a6028c54b751e79a5b1fcd73b", "author": {"user": {"login": "tessaRuckstuhl", "name": "Tessa Ruckstuhl"}}, "url": "https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis/commit/86803544878ed17a6028c54b751e79a5b1fcd73b", "commi